snippet.title: Control Ultimate Edition – Cloud Version – Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Control Ultimate Edition - Cloud Version is available now on Nintendo Switch! Discover a world unknown in the acclaimed action-adventure title from Remedy Entertainment.
